 WILLINGDON WEALTH Overview



												   Willingdon Wealth Management is an investment advisor that manages 268 MM dollars in regulatory AUM and has 9 employees, of which 5 perform investment advisory functions. The manager's has disclosed holdings from 12/31/13 to 03/31/17. The fund's latest filing disclosed 234MM in positions, representing 87% of the manager's regulatory AUM.
												



